User creation
  User enters name and password
  Successful creation logs the user in and navigates to recipe search
User login
  User enters name and password
  Successful login opens recipe search
Recipe search
  User enters included and excluded ingredients
  User selects nutritional ranges
  User selects classifications from a list
  User submits search and is taken to recipe listing
Recipe listing
  Used for both displaying search results and displaying favorited recipes
  Recipe titles and overall ratings appear in a table
  User clicks a recipe title to enter single recipe view
Single recipe view
  Recipe title, description, ratings, classifications, directions, and ingredients text appear on screen
  User can rate the recipe or add as a favorite
  Users can navigate backwards to recipe search
